Usage: runCLP [-help] [-cmd <string>] [-cpf <string>] [-extraLib <string>]
              [-extraVlog <string>] [-post_synthesis] [-setupOnly]
              [-useEEQCellWithLibertyInfo] [-user_config <string>]

-help                               # Prints out the command usage
-cmd <string>                       # user do file (string, optional)
-cpf <string>                       # user CPF (string, optional)
-extraLib <string>                  # extr libraries (string, optional)
-extraVlog <string>                 # extra Verilog (string, optional)
-post_synthesis                     # -post_synthesis mode (bool, optional)
-setupOnly                          # setup only (bool, optional)
-useEEQCellWithLibertyInfo          # use EEQ cell in netlist (bool, optional)
-user_config <string>               # user config file (string, optional)